text: Entacmaea is a genus of sea anemone in the family Actiniidae. ==Species== The following species are recognized in the genus Entacmaea: * Entacmaea medusivora Fautin & Fitt, 1991 * Entacmaea quadricolor (Leuckart in Rüppell & Leuckart, 1828) ==References== Category:Cnidarian genera
title: Entacmaea
